properties.putsql-sql-statement:
INSERT INTO staging (userid, name, age, street, city, state, zip)
VALUES ('${userid}', '${name}', '${age}', '${street}', '${city}', '${state}', '${zip}')
ON CONFLICT (userid) DO UPDATE 
SET name = EXCLUDED.name,
    age = EXCLUDED.age,
    street = EXCLUDED.street,
    city = EXCLUDED.city,
    state = EXCLUDED.state,
    zip = EXCLUDED.zip;
